VERSES (BOOK); THREATS; BUSH, GEORGE; DEMONSTRATIONS -- NEW YORK CITY; 
CENSORSHIP; FREEDOM OF SPEECH; MUSLIMS; FRANCHISES; B DALTON CO; BARNES &amp; 
NOBLE BOOKSTORES INC; PEN (ORGANIZATION) 
</P>
