officers investigating alleged laundering of $1 billion in proceeds from 
cocaine sales. At top, U.S. and Los Angeles officers blocked the entrance to a 
store at 609 S. Hill St. LARRY BESSELL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Below, a 
suspect is placed into a police car at 650 S. Hill. RICK MEYER / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
