Photo, Services for Shooting Victim -- About 150 mourners attended services in 
Boyle Heights for Andrea Denise Garrett, 19, who was fatally shot Feb. 12 in 
Aliso Village housing project. The killing of Garrett, shown in insert, was 
linked to drug dealing in the area and has shocked many in the projects because 
