<P>
Photo, Low road -- Rider finds a bit of Old West ambiance along narrow Porter 
Ranch canyon trail. LAWRENCE K. HO / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
