<DOCNO> LA022389-0065 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 22131 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 23, 1989, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 9A; Column 4; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
