own signs and banners using an office copier. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Bike toy features four sounds and motion-sensitive alarm. KIRK MCCOY / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, The Crusher compacts 12- and 16-ounce cans for 
recycling. 
</P>
