<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022389-0126 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 22324 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 23, 1989, Thursday, Home Edition 
