</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Gary Cole, star of NBC's "Midnight Caller," will turn up in another NBC program 
March 6. He's got the lead role in "Those She Left Behind," a TV movie about a 
businessman whose wife dies, leaving him to care for their newborn child. 
Joining him in the cast are Joanna Kerns (of "Growing Pains"), Colleen Dewhurst 
and Mary Page Keller. 
