<DOCNO> LA022389-0193 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 22493 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 23, 1989, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Orange County Life; Part 9; Page 4; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
45 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHARITY SCORECARD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Sonia Ike, chairwoman of the "Western Hoedown" sponsored by the Cinderella 
Guild of Childrens Hospital of Orange County on Friday night, poses with a car 
on view at premiere of the International Auto Show at Anaheim Stadium. Annual 
event raised an estimated $40,000. 
</P>
