<P>
Pacific Rim Conference Set: San Francisco, where the Golden Gate Bridge 
symbolizes the gateway to the Pacific, was chosen to host a major trade and 
finance symposium expected to attract about 1,000 business and political 
leaders from Pacific Rim nations. Mayor Art Agnos said the 1990 Pacific Rim 
Conference was "a real coup" for San Francisco and would help establish the Bay 
